{"tid":1790310,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《中英聯合聲明》35 週年　英外相促維尼小學一尊尊重條文、與示威者對話","createTime":"2019-12-20T01:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T02:04:08.000Z","uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"980827465e6614ff21923d1faf94c96b06257d90","tid":1790310,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:51:05.000Z","msg":"今日（12 月 19 日）是《中英聯合聲明》簽署 35 週年，英國外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab）發表聲明，促請中國政府跟香港示威者對話，以及尊重《中英聯合聲明》條文。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文在聲明當中提到，「香港正在經歷主權移交以來最長時期的動盪」，而「中英雙方簽署的協議已經清楚說明，香港的高度自治，權利以及自由會維持 50 年不變」。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，藍韜文又說「中國許下的承諾，包括言論自由、司法獨立以及法治制度，對於香港的繁榮以及生活方式都是必要的」。藍韜文表示，作為聯合聲明的其中一方，英國一直認真看待條文當中的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文並且說，「能保證香港未來成功和穩定的唯一方法，就是尊重條文，而且通過有意義的政治對話，去解決香港人的正當訴求」。<br />\n<br />\n在 8 月，藍韜文曾經致電特首林鄭月娥，對香港情況和示威行動表示關注，並促請展開獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n來源：路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hm.people.com.cn/mediafile/200706/19/F200706191123451677944082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhm.people.com.cn%2Fmediafile%2F200706%2F19%2FF200706191123451677944082.jpg&h=6fb1c9c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fd5817893740629b020240e8ba4f5cf60f0dedb","tid":1790310,"uid":113929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:55:45.000Z","msg":"有撚用，得個講"},{"pid":"8bc709db6a9f2558680785b8152d2d1c97bd0704","tid":1790310,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://botanwang.com/sites/default/files/field/image/Clipboard07_344.jpg?itok=_HjA5-bg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbotanwang.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Ffield%2Fimage%2FClipboard07_344.jpg%3Fitok%3D_HjA5-bg&h=25d3c694&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04b171f96f4b46abb7694fe9f550075422758498","tid":1790310,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fd5817893740629b020240e8ba4f5cf60f0dedb","tid":1790310,"uid":113929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:55:45.000Z","msg":"有撚用，得個講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:56:27.000Z","msg":"同 爽爽 同 螢螢<br />\n口交咋  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671626ccc56a26fad9a10a48d91ea3e0eb4802f2","tid":1790310,"uid":107405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:57:46.000Z","msg":"睇死你班垃圾講到2046仲係講緊同一句"},{"pid":"8563c664d2c289f8083f604444338692429834b0","tid":1790310,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:04:08.000Z","msg":"叫藍滔文仆街啦 叫我地同共匪對話 <br />\n5大訴求 缺一不可 好L清楚"}]}